## Bubble Sort

### Algorithm

1. Compare adjacent elements.
2. Swap if larger.
3. Repeat until sorted.

### Code

```python
arr = [5, 3, 1, 4]

for i in range(len(arr)):
    for j in range(len(arr) - 1):
        if arr[j] > arr[j + 1]:
            arr[j], arr[j + 1] = arr[j + 1], arr[j]

print(arr)
```

### Output

```text
[1, 3, 4, 5]
```

